Original Broadway Cast Recording[edit]
The original Broadway cast album was recorded in March 2017 and was released digitally on 21 April and in stores 5 May 2017.[43][44] The album is available from Broadway / Masterworks and is produced by Chris Nightingale, Michael Croiter and Tim Minchin.[45] The songs "Hope", "If I Had My Time Again" and "Seeing You" were released prematurely to download for iTunes, Amazon.com and Spotify.


